### Create an order
POST http://localhost:8080/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "PROD-001"
}

### Get an order (replace {id} with actual orderId)
GET http://localhost:8080/orders/ORD-1775783085188

### Complete an order
DELETE http://localhost:8080/orders/ORD-1775783085188

### Check Prometheus metrics endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/prometheus

### Check specific metric
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/orders.created.total

### Check health
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health
